<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 12:23:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>印度拉贾斯坦邦开始召回部分批次MDH、珠穆朗玛峰香料</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-rajasthan-starts-recalling-some-batches-mdh-everest-spices-2024-06-14/</link><description>印度西部拉贾斯坦邦已开始召回一些批次的流行 MDH 和 Everest 香料，这些香料被发现食用不安全，一位高级官员表示，这是国内和全球对这些品牌日益严格审查的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 11:57:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-rajasthan-starts-recalling-some-batches-mdh-everest-spices-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾军事首长敦促渔民无视中国海警新规定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-chief-urges-fishermen-ignore-chinas-new-coastguard-rules-2024-06-14/</link><description>菲律宾军事首长敦促菲律宾渔民继续在该国南海专属经济区捕鱼，尽管中国海警新规定允许其不经审判拘留非法侵入者，该规定于6月15日生效。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 11:42:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-chief-urges-fishermen-ignore-chinas-new-coastguard-rules-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国可能对欧盟企业征收电动汽车关税进行调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-potential-probes-eu-firms-following-ev-tariffs-2024-06-14/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国企业已要求政府对从欧盟进口的猪肉发起反倾销调查，并对欧盟乳制品发起反补贴调查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:35:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-potential-probes-eu-firms-following-ev-tariffs-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>七国集团警告伊朗核计划持续升级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-warns-iran-over-continuing-nuclear-programme-escalation-2024-06-14/</link><description>根据公报草案，七国集团领导人周五警告伊朗不要推进其核浓缩计划，并表示，如果德黑兰向俄罗斯转让弹道导弹，他们将准备实施新措施。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:19:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-warns-iran-over-continuing-nuclear-programme-escalation-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：消费者检查，但不要忘记法国和日本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-14/</link><description>Alun John 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:02:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>由于需求波动，中国 5 月份新增银行贷款增幅远低于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-new-bank-loans-rise-far-less-than-expected-may-2024-06-14/</link><description>中国5月份新增银行贷款的反弹远低于预期，一些关键货币指标创下历史新低，这表明尽管央行试图提振信心，但世界第二大经济体仍在努力重新站稳脚跟。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 09:53:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-new-bank-loans-rise-far-less-than-expected-may-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡门将呼吁中国球迷停止给他寄钱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/singapore-goalkeeper-urges-chinese-fans-stop-sending-him-money-2024-06-14/</link><description>新加坡国家队门将哈桑·桑尼在新加坡1-3输给泰国的比赛中做出扑救，帮助中国队晋级世界杯预选赛下一轮，他敦促中国球迷停止给他寄钱。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 09:48:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/singapore-goalkeeper-urges-chinese-fans-stop-sending-him-money-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>印度表示对电动汽车征收高关税是为了防止中国进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/india-says-high-tariffs-evs-protect-chinese-imports-2024-06-14/</link><description>印度贸易部门周五表示，在欧盟等其他主要经济体对中国电动汽车征收关税之际，该国的汽车市场通过对电动汽车进口征收高关税而“得到了很好的保护”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 09:48:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/india-says-high-tariffs-evs-protect-chinese-imports-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>监管机构称特斯拉将修复中国 5,836 辆进口汽车的软件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-software-5836-imported-cars-china-watchdog-says-2024-06-14/</link><description>中国市场监管机构周五表示，特斯拉将以安全问题为由，将从 7 月起修复 5,836 辆进口 Model 3、Model S 和 Model X 汽车的软件。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 08:36:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-software-5836-imported-cars-china-watchdog-says-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>德国表示中国需要在电动汽车关税争端中采取“认真行动”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/germany-trying-prevent-or-soften-eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-bloomberg-news-says-2024-06-14/</link><description>德国政府发言人周五表示，德国希望中国在进口电动汽车关税问题上采取“认真行动”，并希望未来几周的谈判能够避免不断升级的贸易冲突。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 08:08:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/germany-trying-prevent-or-soften-eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-bloomberg-news-says-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，恒大清算律师事务所正在调查普华永道等公司的潜在索赔</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/evergrande-liquidation-law-firm-probing-pwc-others-potential-claims-sources-say-2024-06-14/</link><description>三名消息人士称，中国恒大集团清算人任命的律师正在调查该房地产开发商的一些服务提供商，包括其前审计师普华永道，以可能为债权人挽回损失。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 08:04:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/evergrande-liquidation-law-firm-probing-pwc-others-potential-claims-sources-say-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>由于利润率压力、人民币疲软阻碍政策宽松，中国将维持关键利率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-set-hold-key-rate-margin-pressure-weaker-yuan-hamper-policy-easing-2024-06-14/</link><description>路透调查显示，市场普遍预计中国央行下周一展期到期中期贷款时将维持关键政策利率不变。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 06:59:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-set-hold-key-rate-margin-pressure-weaker-yuan-hamper-policy-easing-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国高级外交官警告中国举动引发意外冲突的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/senior-us-diplomat-warns-risks-accidental-conflict-sparked-by-chinas-moves-2024-06-14/</link><description>华盛顿驻台北高级外交官周五表示，中国在台湾、日本和南中国海周围的“挑衅”行动存在发生事故的风险，可能无意中引发更广泛的冲突。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 06:42:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/senior-us-diplomat-warns-risks-accidental-conflict-sparked-by-chinas-moves-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国制造业团体呼吁加强对中国进口产品的保护</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-manufacturing-group-calls-stronger-protection-against-chinese-imports-2024-06-14/</link><description>在美国总统乔·拜登对中国电动汽车、太阳能电池板和其他战略商品征收高额关税后，由美国钢铁工人联合会和国内制造商领导的一个政策小组呼吁美国对中国进口产品实施更严格的贸易壁垒。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 06:37:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-manufacturing-group-calls-stronger-protection-against-chinese-imports-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>债券收益率下降让中国央行面临艰难抉择</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/falling-bond-yields-leave-chinas-central-bank-facing-tough-call-2024-06-14/</link><description>中国央行在债券市场上涨中遏制金融稳定风险的决心正面临迫在眉睫的考验，因为它描绘的软增长和低通胀的长期前景与其对经济的看法背道而驰。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 06:19:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/falling-bond-yields-leave-chinas-central-bank-facing-tough-call-2024-06-14/</guid></item></channel></rss>